Oasis Pronovias Privée 2022 is a luxurious
collection created by @alessandrarinaudo for the bride looking for something unique and spectacular ✨

Taking inspiration from exotic foliage and striking oriental architecture, lace and embroidery head in mesmerizing new directions, and stunning haute couture accents adorn a variety of lightweight silhouettes. 

Link in bio to see the full collection and book your appointment 😍

#Pronovias #OASIScollection #WeddingDress
